ibid, lateral view (left = dorsal); 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1314,1340,1874,1898]" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">H,</emphasis>
aedeagal complex, dorsal view; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[380,397,1910,1934]" pageId="5" pageNumber="406">I,</emphasis>
